---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Father's Heart Bible — Spirit Media"
	description="The Father's Heart Bible™ — an intimate translation revealing our Father's heart to a fatherless generation."
>
	<main id="main-content">

		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="bg-red-600 text-white py-24 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-200 mb-4">
					A Spirit Media Project
				</p>
				<h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4">
					Father's Heart Bible™
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl font-medium text-red-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-6">
					An Intimate Translation Revealing Our Father's Heart to a Fatherless Generation
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
					<a
						href="https://fathersheartbible.com"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors"
					>
						Visit FathersHeartBible.com →
					</a>
					<a
						href="#about"
						class="inline-block border-2 border-white text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors"
					>
						Learn More
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- MAIN INTRO -->
		<section id="about" class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
					For centuries, millions have read the Bible faithfully — and connected to God as a
					servant to a master rather than as a beloved son to a loving Father.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Jesus said, "No one comes to the Father except through me." The destination was never
					merely forgiveness or heaven. The destination has always been our Father — and His heart.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
					The Father's Heart Bible™ is a new interpretive English translation that faithfully
					renders the original Hebrew, Aramaic, and Greek texts while clearly revealing God's
					identity as our Father — and His heart toward His children — throughout Scripture.
					It fills a gap no other translation addresses.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- BEYOND NAME TO HEART -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Beyond Name to Heart</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					The Father's Heart Bible doesn't merely reveal the Father's name — it reveals His heart.
					A Father who:
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
					{
						[
							'Pursues His children with relentless love.',
							'Delights in them with singing and joy.',
							'Grieves when they wander.',
							'Runs to embrace them when they return.',
							'Invites them home with arms wide open.',
						].map((item) => (
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
								<span class="text-red-600 mt-1">•</span>
								{item}
							</li>
						))
					}
				</ul>
				<blockquote class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-600 p-6 rounded-r-xl">
					<p class="font-serif text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 italic leading-relaxed">
						"Come home. You belong to Me. You are My beloved child."
					</p>
					<cite class="mt-2 block text-sm text-red-600 font-semibold not-italic">
						One message for every reader
					</cite>
				</blockquote>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- PLACE HIS WORD IN THE NATIONS -->
		<section class="bg-navy-950 text-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Place His Word in the Nations</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
					Each gift of $100 places three Father's Heart Bibles into the hands of readers worldwide
					— empowering them to hear their Father's voice for the first time.
				</p>
				<a
					href="https://fathersheartbible.com"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="inline-block bg-red-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors"
				>
					Visit FathersHeartBible.com →
				</a>
				<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-4">Published by Spirit Media.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
